
EasyAlign is a very nice plugin
See https://github.com/junegunn/vim-easy-align

Summary:  start by loading plugins:
(see curl -fLo ~/.vim/autoload/plug.vim --create-dirs https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim)
Instructions there on what to put in .vimrc, and then to align text, try putting the cursor inside a chunk and use
vipga|
to align on |

Note that this will align on only 1.  So you might prefer vipga*|
